    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all maintenance records up to date and every feature functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a car that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
