    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner ready to tackle significant repairs. The exterior has seen better days, with visible rust on the wheel arches, several large dents, and paint that is peeling in multiple areas. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and passenger window motor, are currently non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable leak and the transmission shifts roughly, meaning it likely needs major service before it can be considered a reliable driver. This is a project car sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
