    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unrivaled distinction, maintained to a showroom-grade standard that reflects an uncompromising commitment to preservation. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and an interior environment that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning collector a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in pristine, investment-grade condition.",
